methods.name: GetControllerRecenterCount(Controller controllerMask)
methods.summary: Returns the number of times the controller has been recentered this session. Useful for detecting recenter events and resetting state such as arm model simulations, etc. Wraps around to 0 after 255. Only applicable to controllers that require recentering, such as the GearVR Controller. Returns 0 for controllers that do not require recentering.
methods.syntax: public static byte GetControllerRecenterCount(Controller controllerMask)
methods.linkedSyntax: public static byte GetControllerRecenterCount(Controller controllerMask)
